## Performance Tuning

### Increase Replicas

```bash
# Update values.yaml
backend:
  replicaCount: 5  # was 3

frontend:
  replicaCount: 5  # was 3

# Upgrade
helm upgrade registration-app helm/registration-app/ -f helm/registration-app/values.yaml -n registration-app
```

### Adjust HPA Thresholds

```bash
# In values.yaml
hpa:
  backend:
    minReplicas: 3
    maxReplicas: 20  # was 10
    targetCPUUtilizationPercentage: 70  # was 80
    targetMemoryUtilizationPercentage: 70  # was 80

# Upgrade
helm upgrade registration-app helm/registration-app/ -f helm/registration-app/values.yaml -n registration-app
```

### Adjust Resource Requests/Limits

```bash
# In values.yaml
backend:
  resources:
    requests:
      cpu: 250m      # was 100m
      memory: 256Mi  # was 128Mi
    limits:
      cpu: 500m      # was 500m
      memory: 512Mi  # was 512Mi

# Upgrade
helm upgrade registration-app helm/registration-app/ -f helm/registration-app/values.yaml -n registration-app
```

